{"tid":765844,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港旅行有咩野推介","createTime":"2018-08-03T06:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T06:02:34.000Z","uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c751fdb734bdc77645569f66832bbb109e2fc720","tid":765844,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"最好有眼前一亮既景點或奇異體會,至於單純影一張相果類就可免側免<br />\n<br />\n舉例:<br />\n簡簡單單既志蓮淨苑好合我心水,方便易去又有野睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/135939_c64e58257c59a669a0adf8e27c0d24e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F135939_c64e58257c59a669a0adf8e27c0d24e5.jpg&h=5cb8f71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於單純打卡影相比如彩虹邨呢D就真係好失望<br />\n<br />\n有無咩野好推介,比如大型二手市場或舊店,展覽都好OK"}]}